<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/html" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/html" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/html">
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type">

</head>
<body style="color: #000000;font-size: 14px;font-family: Verdana,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">
<table width="100%" id="background" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
  <tr><td align="center" valign="top" style="color: #000000;font-size: 14px;font-family: Verdana,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">
    <table width="650" id="main" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="20">
      <tr>
        <td id="header" colspan="2" style="color: #000000;font-size: 14px;font-family: Verdana,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;text-align:center;">
          <a href="https://www.tailoredrepublic.com"><img src="https://d195zx82sfk1xc.cloudfront.net/assets/logos/logo-shield.png" width="443" height="66" alt="Tailored Republic"></a>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td colspan="2" style="color: #000000;font-size: 14px;font-family: Verdana,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">
          <p>Hey <%= @referee.first_name %>,</p>
          <p>Thanks for creating an account with Tailored Republic. Because you were referred by <%= @referrer.name %>,
            we are hooking you up with $<%= Referral.credit_amount %> off your first suit or shirt purchase. It will be applied
            automatically at checkout so go ahead and start customizing your first TR
            suit: <%= link_to 'https://www.tailoredrepublic.com/shop/suits', 'https://www.tailoredrepublic.com/shop/suits' %>
          </p>
          <p>If you like Tailored Republic as much as <%= @referrer.name %>, you should go ahead and invite your friends
            using your own personal referral link:</p>
          <p><%= link_to @referee.referral_url, @referee.referral_url %></p>
          <p>You will receive $<%= Referral.credit_amount %> for every friend that you refer that signs up and purchases
            any of the Tailored Republic collection.
          </p>
          <p>Let us know if you have any questions!</p>
          <p>Stay dapper,<br/>
            The Tailored Republic Team
          </p>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <%= render 'shared/email_social_media_dock' %>
      <tr>
        <td id="footer" colspan="2" align="center" style="color: #555555;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">
          <p>&copy;2013 Tailored Republic // <%= link_to 'www.tailoredrepublic.com', 'https://www.tailoredrepublic.com' %></p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </td></tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>